---
title: Saucy Tikka-Style Chicken Breast Sandwiches with Indian-Spiced Potatoes
description: There's nothing basic about this chicken sandwich! Tangy cucumber salad and chicken thighs coated in fragrant tikka sauce are the perfect combo, all wrapped up in a soft bun. On the side, Indian-spiced roasted potatoes are yours for the dipping into a DIY tikka mayo.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saucy-tikka-style-chicken-breast-sandwiches-cb7c17f7.jpg
